author: StevenTheBrick
title: Super Heroes Lab
review:
1/5

 I got this really cheap, but that doesn't excuse it for the price being at $30. $5 or $10 off would've been better. The parts are mediocre for a Duplo build that is supposed to be a "Lab." The building experience did not exist due to building random things and calling it a "Lab." Even for the Duplo age range, the playability basically comes from the motorcycle and the characters.
